---
title: Herby Lamb Meatballs with Buttery Mash with Roasted Grape Pan Sauce
description: Rich and flavourful lamb meatballs get a quick coating with a sticky blistered grape and balsamic pan sauce. Buttery Mash and Brussel sprouts spruce up this lamb dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/herby-lamb-meatballs-with-buttery-mash-04e8ab54.jpg
